   SPORTS
</P>
<P>
   (Moved in `s' category)
</P>
<P>
   CAR-INDY (Indianapolis) _ Brack's victory in Indy 500 does
compute, to the gallon. By Tarik El-Bashir.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-KNICKS-PACERS (Indianapolis) _ This time, Ewing buries
Miller and the Pacers. By Selena Roberts.
</P>
<P>
   With photos.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-KNICK-VETERANS (Indianapolis) _ A new Knicks' team relies on
