</P>
<P>
   BKN-PACERS (Indianapolis) _ At least for a game, `Curse of
Reggie' lifts. By Joe Drape.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-SPURS-ROBINSON (San Antonio) _ Robinson takes control of the
ship. By Chris Broussard.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-BERKOW-COLUMN (Indianapolis) _ A missed shot and a soap
opera in game one. By Ira Berkow.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-PLAYOFF-FATIGUE (Toronto) _ Overtime, TV and
air-conditioning. By Joe Lapointe.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-METS-DIAMONDBACKS (New York) _ Randy Johnson unsettles the
Mets' lineup even more. By Jason Diamos.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-DIAMONDBACKS (New York) _ Big budget earns big benefit for
Diamondbacks. By Murray Chass.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKS-JAYS (Toronto) _ At-bat by at-bat, Jeter's star is
ascendant. By Buster Olney.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-INDIANS (Undated) _ Roberto Alomar adds skills, thrills and
victories to Indians. By Murray Chass.
</P>
