<HEADLINE>
DRIVING GUN CONTROL: IT'S ABOUT THE ELECTIONS, STUPID 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(jt) 
 By FRANK BRUNI    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
