<HEADLINE>
HEY, ALLIES, FOLLOW ME. I'VE GOT ALL THE NEW TOYS. 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(jt) 
 By CRAIG R. WHITNEY    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   NATO's bombing campaign in Yugoslavia has exposed more than
