<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-31 15:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7359 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FOREIGN-JOURNAL-BOS &LR;      05-31 0663
