<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; For Immediate Release &LR;  &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   The Boston Globe plans to move the following FEATURE stories for
use by N.Y. Times News Service clients. For questions about
stories, contact  &UR; Roy Greene  &LR; at the Boston Globe,  &UR; 617-929-2597. &LR;
</P>
<P>
   All stories will bear the BOS designator.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; CONFLICT IN THE BALKANS &LR;   &UR; (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   YUGO-DEATHTOLL (Undated) _ At what point does the bombing's
civilian death toll _ even if the civilians are mainly Serbs rather
than Kosovar Albanians _ become unacceptably high? By Fred Kaplan.
1580 words.
</P>
<P>
