<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-31 15:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7361 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CULTURE-LLBEAN-BOS &LR;      05-31 1270
