<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-31 15:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7384 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WHITE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      05-31 0643
