 &QL; 
COMPUTER-COLUMN (Phoenix) - Guess what? CompuServe is still alive!
OK, maybe you didn't think it was dead. But chances are, you
haven't given it much thought over the past few years, which is why
it's had so much trouble. What I like about the new CompuServe is
that it's been streamlined. Pages are clean and crisp. Navigation
is simple, thanks to a menu bar at the top. And because it's geared
toward adults, CompuServe lacks the annoying kiddie stuff you'll
find on AOL. By DAVID HOYE. Story moved in the ``F'' category. &QL;
