the first game of the NBA eastern conference playoffs on Sunday.
The second match in the best of seven series is Tuesday night.
(Barton Silverman/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT6) NEW YORK -- May 31, 1999 -- HARE-INTERVIEW, 5-31 --
Playwright David Hare backstage at the Booth Theater. His play Via
